oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Making Plans - Wilburn Brothers - 1963-11-18
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of Making Plans, written by Johnny Russell and Voni Morrison, produced by Owen Bradley, recorded at Columbia Recording Studio in Nashville, Tenn. on November 18, 1963, and performed by the Wilburn Brothers, Bob Moore (bass), and other unknown musicians. Most likely commercial recording (Decca 31674).
